@startuml
title NILM Pipeline (Activity Diagram)

' ---------------------------
' Meter Data Source (read only)
' ---------------------------
|Meter Data Storage (DB)|
start
:Query consumption data\n(from SQL / Influx-like DB);
:Retrieve records\n(3-minute granularity);

' ---------------------------
' Ingestion + Preparation
' ---------------------------
|Data Ingestion & Preparation|
:Validate data\n(check format & completeness);

if (Data valid?) then (Yes)
  :Format conversion, resampling,\nnormalization;
  :Forward prepared data to inference;
else (No)
  :Create validation log entry;
  |Historical SQL Storage|
  :Store log record\n(validation failure);
  stop
endif

' ---------------------------
' Inference
' ---------------------------
|Model Inference|
:Run NILM inference\n(load latest model if needed);
:Perform disaggregation;
:Generate appliance-level results;

' ---------------------------
' Historical storage
' ---------------------------
|Historical SQL Storage|
:Store disaggregation results;
:Store processing logs;

' ---------------------------
' Dashboard / visualization
' ---------------------------
|Dashboard / Visualization|
:Query historical SQL storage;
:Display results on dashboard;

stop
@enduml
